dct_description_sm: Map shows international boundaries, roads, and railroads. Title devised by cataloger. Map shows emblem of Fatah with text: [fath al thawrat masīrat al taṣbih]. Map shows emblem of Fatah with text: فتح الثورة مسيرة التصحيح. At bottom (approximate transliteration and translation): [la namlik alla hayaatan wahidatan nahabaha lilwaṭan -- hadiat fatah althawra = We only have one life to give to the homeland -- A gift that opened the revolution]. لا نملك الّا حياة واحدة نهبها للوطن -- هدية فتحا الثورة At bottom (approximate transliteration and translation): [la namlik alla hayaatan wahidatan nahabaha lilwaṭan -- hadiat fatah althawra = We only have one life to give to the homeland -- A gift that opened the revolution]
